title: New CLEAR alert system aims to help missing Texans between 18-65
sentence: It's called a CLEAR Alert, and one Coastal Bend mother whose daughter was murdered is praising the lawmakers who passed the bill.

title: New CLEAR alert system aims to help missing Texans between 18-65
sentence: Fallon Wood, the mother of 21-year-old Breanna Wood who was found murdered back in 2016, believes if this type of alert had been available when her own daughter first went missing, it might have made a difference.
